trpzSystemMib.name: trpzSystemMib

revisions.description: v3.0.1: Added new objects to support Power Supply status. (for 6.2 release)
v2.1.0: Obsoleted two previously deprecated objects (for 6.2 release)
v2.0.0: Added new objects to support CPU load and memory (RAM) usage details: for last few seconds (''instant''), minute, 5 minutes, hour, day, 3 days (for 6.0 release)

TrpzSysPowerSupplyStatus.name: TrpzSysPowerSupplyStatus
TrpzSysPowerSupplyStatus.description: The status of a Power Supply.

trpzSysCpuMemoryUsedBytes.name: trpzSysCpuMemoryUsedBytes
trpzSysCpuMemoryUsedBytes.description: CPU memory used in bytes. Obsoleted by trpzSysCpuMemoryInstantUsage.

trpzSysCpuMemoryTotalBytes.name: trpzSysCpuMemoryTotalBytes
trpzSysCpuMemoryTotalBytes.description: CPU total physical memory in bytes. Obsoleted by trpzSysCpuMemorySize.

trpzSysCpuAverageLoad.name: trpzSysCpuAverageLoad
trpzSysCpuAverageLoad.description: CPU load average since system startup.

trpzSysCpuMemorySize.name: trpzSysCpuMemorySize
trpzSysCpuMemorySize.description: Maximum available CPU Memory (RAM) in KBytes. This is the memory available to the Wireless Switch software. May be less than physical RAM size.

trpzSysCpuInstantLoad.name: trpzSysCpuInstantLoad
trpzSysCpuInstantLoad.description: CPU instant load (for last few seconds).

trpzSysCpuMemoryInstantUsage.name: trpzSysCpuMemoryInstantUsage
trpzSysCpuMemoryInstantUsage.description: Instant memory usage (RAM) in KBytes (for last few seconds). Ranges between 0 and trpzSysCpuMemorySize.

trpzSysCpuMemoryLastMinuteUsage.name: trpzSysCpuMemoryLastMinuteUsage
trpzSysCpuMemoryLastMinuteUsage.description: Memory usage (RAM) for last minute in KBytes. Ranges between 0 and trpzSysCpuMemorySize.

trpzSysCpuMemoryLast5MinutesUsage.name: trpzSysCpuMemoryLast5MinutesUsage
trpzSysCpuMemoryLast5MinutesUsage.description: Memory usage (RAM) for last 5 minutes in KBytes. Ranges between 0 and trpzSysCpuMemorySize.

trpzSysCpuMemoryLastHourUsage.name: trpzSysCpuMemoryLastHourUsage
trpzSysCpuMemoryLastHourUsage.description: Memory usage (RAM) for last hour in KBytes. Ranges between 0 and trpzSysCpuMemorySize.

trpzSysCpuMemoryLastDayUsage.name: trpzSysCpuMemoryLastDayUsage
trpzSysCpuMemoryLastDayUsage.description: Memory usage (RAM) for last day in KBytes. Ranges between 0 and trpzSysCpuMemorySize.

trpzSysCpuMemoryLast3DaysUsage.name: trpzSysCpuMemoryLast3DaysUsage
trpzSysCpuMemoryLast3DaysUsage.description: Memory usage (RAM) for last 3 days in KBytes. Ranges between 0 and trpzSysCpuMemorySize.

trpzSysNumPowerSuppliesSupported.name: trpzSysNumPowerSuppliesSupported
trpzSysNumPowerSuppliesSupported.description: The number of power supplies supported by the Wireless Switch. This is the upper limit of the number of entries in the power supply table, trpzSysPowerSupplyTable.

trpzSysPowerSupplyTable.name: trpzSysPowerSupplyTable
trpzSysPowerSupplyTable.description: Table of power supplies actually installed on the Wireless Switch.

trpzSysPowerSupplyEntry.name: trpzSysPowerSupplyEntry
trpzSysPowerSupplyEntry.description: An entry in the trpzSysPowerSupplyTable table.

trpzSysPowerSupplyDeviceOID.name: trpzSysPowerSupplyDeviceOID
trpzSysPowerSupplyDeviceOID.description: OID value used to identify this chassis component as indicated in Registration MIB.

trpzSysPowerSupplyDescr.name: trpzSysPowerSupplyDescr
trpzSysPowerSupplyDescr.description: A human interpretable description of this power supply, for example 'Left Power Supply'.
